Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.01,0:59:23.11,英文,,0,0,0,,And let me just highlight a few of these lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.11,0:59:26.79,英文,,0,0,0,,The very first line is what's called your document type declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.79,0:59:28.81,英文,,0,0,0,,Doesn't really matter to remember that by phrasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.81,0:59:36.44,英文,,0,0,0,,And this is just something you copy, paste, or do from memory at the top of any .html file that you create when making your own web page.
